{"tid":617682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣鬧市 男童高處墮下送院搶救","createTime":"2018-04-05T07:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T11:00:32.000Z","uid":28366,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0edf5d99bea924692115c959f041e9bc5b645a1d","tid":617682,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/151509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F151509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aba03934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/151512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F151512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c4a89674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/151514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F151514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d94aff71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/151516_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F151516_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d214d872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔登龍街49號金龍大廈，下午1時10分，有途人報警指一名4至5歲南亞裔男童，倒卧大廈1樓簷篷，懷疑他由上址4樓單位墮下。救護員趕至時，男童仍有知覺，父親在他身邊，隨即將他抱起送院搶救，警方正了解其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n在附近食店工作的一名女員工表示，「男童唔醒，佢爸爸抱起佢時昏迷，阿Sir衝上樓梯，幫佢（男童父）抱住男童落嚟送院。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180405/58036614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F58036614&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0Ljk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvd